{"tid":1798852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[突發] 立法會議員張華峰女兒　半山地利根德里墮斃","createTime":"2019-12-26T13:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T19:23:17.000Z","uid":61161,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c5968bc4018d50231360d281f20adc184681f7","tid":1798852,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191226/mobile/bkn-20191226152233508-1226_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191226%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191226152233508-1226_00822_001.html&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=99c4ef12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191226/mobile/bkn-20191226152233508-1226_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員張華峰女兒　半山地利根德里墮斃<br />\n<br />\n半山地利根德里世紀大廈女子墮樓亡。今日(26日)下午1時44分，上址一名保安人員突然聽聞巨響，循聲查看，發現一名女子昏迷倒臥於花槽位置，懷疑她從高處墮下，於是報警求助。救援人員接報到場，證實女子已當場死亡，毋須送院。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查後相信死者為立法會議員張華峰的其中一名女兒(22歲)，事件沒有可疑，惟死因有待驗屍後確定。張華峰回應表示，女兒患躁鬱症，有看醫生，已超過兩年。<br />\n<br />\n事件無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfa101e1f80fce21c1331dcd00b7ccc93f5cd1e","tid":1798852,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"深紅<br />\n<br />\n公職<br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員、香港證券學會會長、香港中華總商會選任會董、中華海外聯誼會理事、香港友好協進會董事、廣東省工商聯合會常務委員、香港立法會議員、香港福建社團聯會永遠名譽會長，以及監警會副主席。"},{"pid":"8fda599f885b9dbb8d3cb474c830b67c3a49a893","tid":1798852,"uid":134323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"暗殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a502458be5412082e5a25e1357d8daa95972d577","tid":1798852,"uid":44298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"check返佢係爆麥美娟爆粗鬧林病果條友，唔知係唔係有人報復"},{"pid":"02b2b83179c5332c16d84cbeb1d8f692b9b9772d","tid":1798852,"uid":52090,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 事件沒有可疑，<br />\n22歲，會唔會係手足，但因為反送中，比老豆同Popo夾埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b22e03d102bcad117f7a3c7f108d715c3b54f7d","tid":1798852,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:01:07.000Z","msg":"恭喜恭喜"},{"pid":"b501341200e13e3dbee4c1f36e20e577aab9becb","tid":1798852,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8fda599f885b9dbb8d3cb474c830b67c3a49a893","tid":1798852,"uid":134323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"暗殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"無可疑呀"},{"pid":"3f0b88d203cdc0ce700963d7303038d0f2abf49f","tid":1798852,"uid":70551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"藍絲連自己個女都唔放過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda9dd4af5650652662253f21d135ca8e93ba156","tid":1798852,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:21:49.000Z","msg":"在將軍澳停車場墮樓重傷的科技大學學生周梓樂延至今日（8日）不治，終年22歲。民主派立法會議員下午在立法會內會開始時站內默哀，原已到場的金融服務界張華峰離席，建制派在默哀後才進入會議室<br />\n<br />\n佢個女都係22歲"},{"pid":"5c6ff845970f34f25c91973fe1f59999b64807cc","tid":1798852,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnYKeWt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnYKeWt.jpg&h=0f34dcbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48d3f0573845265b6d2f9eb06fc0f8b1f9826e6f","tid":1798852,"uid":65074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:26:09.000Z","msg":"mon po嘅五毛<br />\n麻煩同你地上司講聲<br />\n<br />\n我地唔識立法會班垃圾嘅仔女<br />\n唔會有感覺